1
00:00:08,410 --> 00:00:10,240
<font color="yellow">(Episode 17)</font>

2
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:12,370
<font color="yellow">The truth that can't be punished by the law.</font>

3
00:00:13,510 --> 00:00:15,840
<font color="yellow">The truth that has no choice but to rely on a good conscience.</font>

4
00:00:16,610 --> 00:00:18,770
<font color="yellow">I chased after the truth...</font>

5
00:00:19,310 --> 00:00:20,840
<font color="yellow">to hear a sincere apology.</font>

6
00:00:21,670 --> 00:00:24,370
<font color="yellow">This spread wider than I thought.</font>

7
00:00:26,770 --> 00:00:28,910
<font color="yellow">- Keep the camera steady.
-  Got it.</font>

8
00:00:30,510 --> 00:00:32,140
<font color="yellow">Are you drunk?</font>

9
00:00:36,740 --> 00:00:39,310
<font color="yellow">Don't ever step a foot in my operating room.</font>

10
00:00:40,010 --> 00:00:41,040
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

11
00:00:45,010 --> 00:00:46,600
<font color="yellow">- She's bleeding.
-  Suction.</font>

12
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:47,840
<font color="yellow">Call and ask for blood.</font>

13
00:00:49,470 --> 00:00:50,640
<font color="yellow">We need blood urgently.</font>

14
00:01:00,310 --> 00:01:01,570
<font color="yellow">I think you'll have to open the abdomen.</font>

15
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:07,040
<font color="yellow">She's in shock.</font>

16
00:01:09,340 --> 00:01:10,510
<font color="yellow">Her blood pressure is dropping.</font>

17
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,040
<font color="yellow">- Let's do it.
-  Okay.</font>

18
00:01:19,910 --> 00:01:20,940
<font color="yellow">It's a cardiac arrest.</font>

19
00:01:21,570 --> 00:01:22,570
<font color="yellow">Start pumping.</font>

20
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:35,870
<font color="yellow">I don't know how my life will change...</font>

21
00:01:36,940 --> 00:01:37,970
<font color="yellow">the moment I find out the truth.</font>

22
00:01:40,210 --> 00:01:42,340
<font color="yellow">(Gukil Medical Centre)</font>

23
00:01:42,340 --> 00:01:43,510
<font color="yellow">(57th Disciplinary Committee Meeting)</font>

24
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:46,940
<font color="yellow">We will now begin the disciplinary meeting for Dr Yoo Hye Jung...</font>

25
00:01:46,940 --> 00:01:48,950
<font color="yellow">for damaging the reputation of Gukil Medical Centre...</font>

26
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:52,810
<font color="yellow">as the Congressman's doctor.</font>

27
00:01:53,340 --> 00:01:54,640
<font color="yellow">First, I'd like to thank you.</font>

28
00:01:56,310 --> 00:01:59,740
<font color="yellow">I personally think it's an honour...</font>

29
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:01,640
<font color="yellow">to be someone influential enough...</font>

30
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,570
<font color="yellow">to damage the reputation of this hospital.</font>

31
00:02:07,970 --> 00:02:10,840
<font color="yellow">You are the Congressman's doctor, aren't you?</font>

32
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:12,370
<font color="yellow">Yes, I am.</font>

33
00:02:12,370 --> 00:02:14,950
<font color="yellow">Why weren't you able to respond...</font>

34
00:02:14,950 --> 00:02:16,810
<font color="yellow">when he complained about being in pain?</font>

35
00:02:16,810 --> 00:02:19,470
<font color="yellow">I was operating on a patient with a ruptured cerebral aneurysm.</font>

36
00:02:20,110 --> 00:02:23,110
<font color="yellow">I asked a fellow doctor to respond to his calls during the surgery...</font>

37
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:24,400
<font color="yellow">before starting the operation.</font>

38
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:26,140
<font color="yellow">Why are you bringing up someone else right now?</font>

39
00:02:26,510 --> 00:02:28,880
<font color="yellow">The problem is that you handed your responsibilities to someone else.</font>

40
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:31,620
<font color="yellow">Did you have to operate on the patient at that exact time?</font>

41
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:33,350
<font color="yellow">It was my patient,</font>

42
00:02:33,350 --> 00:02:37,550
<font color="yellow">and a ruptured cerebral aneurysm is like a time bomb.</font>

43
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:38,710
<font color="yellow">I couldn't delay it.</font>

44
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,440
<font color="yellow">Does this mean that you think...</font>

45
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:44,950
<font color="yellow">you did nothing wrong in regards to what happened to the Congressman?</font>

46
00:02:44,950 --> 00:02:46,280
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

47
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:49,670
<font color="yellow">I'm thankful that you think of me as such an important person,</font>

48
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:52,740
<font color="yellow">but I believe I made the right choice.</font>

49
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:01,530
<font color="yellow">Isn't this unfair?</font>

50
00:03:01,530 --> 00:03:02,870
<font color="yellow">Why should Dr Yoo get disciplinary action?</font>

51
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:04,810
<font color="yellow">I know. They should blame Dr Jin.</font>

52
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,840
<font color="yellow">He's leaving his daughter out.</font>

53
00:03:07,210 --> 00:03:10,040
<font color="yellow">This is unfair for people without parents in high places.</font>

54
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:13,440
<font color="yellow">Do you know what you call that?</font>

55
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:15,610
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

56
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,310
<font color="yellow">You scared me.</font>

57
00:03:18,170 --> 00:03:19,210
<font color="yellow">Hi.</font>

58
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:23,120
<font color="yellow">What is this weird vibe?</font>

59
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,170
<font color="yellow">- No.
-  That can't be.</font>

60
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,240
<font color="yellow">Why would we?</font>

61
00:03:28,010 --> 00:03:31,010
<font color="yellow">- Tell me what's going on.
-  We were just...</font>

62
00:03:31,810 --> 00:03:35,610
<font color="yellow">talking about how sad we are that Dr Yoo is getting punished.</font>

63
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:36,670
<font color="yellow">Isn't that right?</font>

64
00:03:39,340 --> 00:03:41,260
<font color="yellow">Go check Patient Lee Tae Sik's dressing.</font>

65
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:42,470
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

66
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:49,610
<font color="yellow">Dr Jin, the President would like to see you.</font>

67
00:03:58,340 --> 00:03:59,410
<font color="yellow">Come in.</font>

68
00:04:09,210 --> 00:04:11,770
<font color="yellow">Are you still upset with me? Why are you avoiding me?</font>

69
00:04:12,310 --> 00:04:14,130
<font color="yellow">Weren't you in the disciplinary committee meeting?</font>

70
00:04:14,130 --> 00:04:15,740
<font color="yellow">We're done hearing the explanation of the person in question.</font>

71
00:04:15,740 --> 00:04:17,470
<font color="yellow">We'll decide on a disciplinary action after lunch.</font>

72
00:04:17,910 --> 00:04:20,270
<font color="yellow">I'm going to bring this up when we make the decision.</font>

73
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:26,660
<font color="yellow">(Yoo Hye Jung)</font>

74
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:29,810
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you tell me Prof. Hong was your high school teacher...</font>

75
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:32,840
<font color="yellow">and that Dr Yoo is the one responsible for your burns?</font>

76
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:35,510
<font color="yellow">Please don't bring this up.</font>

77
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:38,610
<font color="yellow">I don't want to get involved because of this.</font>

78
00:04:38,610 --> 00:04:40,540
<font color="yellow">Why wouldn't I use such a good opportunity?</font>

79
00:04:41,270 --> 00:04:43,380
<font color="yellow">I'm here to compliment you.</font>

80
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:45,510
<font color="yellow">I've put you through too hard of a training.</font>

81
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:46,770
<font color="yellow">What am I to you?</font>

82
00:04:47,570 --> 00:04:49,880
<font color="yellow">You gave me the stick last time. Is this my carrot?</font>

83
00:04:50,810 --> 00:04:52,770
<font color="yellow">I don't want your compliments any longer.</font>

84
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:56,510
<font color="yellow">I couldn't get any sleep after slapping you.</font>

85
00:04:57,540 --> 00:05:01,310
<font color="yellow">- Do you know how much I love you?
-  I want you to leave it alone.</font>

86
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,540
<font color="yellow">This is my weakness.</font>

87
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:07,040
<font color="yellow">Do you know how long I was in pain because of this?</font>

88
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,470
<font color="yellow">I'm going to kill myself if you bring this up.</font>

89
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:38,610
<font color="yellow">Are you going somewhere?</font>

90
00:05:39,010 --> 00:05:41,780
<font color="yellow">I will face disciplinary action. It's just a matter of how bad it is.</font>

91
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:43,010
<font color="yellow">I'm getting ready for it.</font>

92
00:05:43,810 --> 00:05:45,240
<font color="yellow">Do you think this is my fault?</font>

93
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:49,270
<font color="yellow">Yes, I do.</font>

94
00:05:50,010 --> 00:05:52,610
<font color="yellow">You handed him over to Yeong Gook when I asked you.</font>

95
00:05:55,570 --> 00:05:57,970
<font color="yellow">But I can't get anything done if I think that.</font>

96
00:05:58,340 --> 00:06:00,770
<font color="yellow">- So I won't blame you.
-  Then what?</font>

97
00:06:01,740 --> 00:06:02,870
<font color="yellow">I was unlucky.</font>

98
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,840
<font color="yellow">I was scared for a second.</font>

99
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:11,670
<font color="yellow">I thought you had feelings just like me...</font>

100
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:15,020
<font color="yellow">and that it'd only be normal for you to blame me.</font>

101
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:16,340
<font color="yellow">But you're different.</font>

102
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:19,970
<font color="yellow">Are you hurt this time because I don't blame you?</font>

103
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:23,850
<font color="yellow">Does everyone else around you blame others in these situations?</font>

104
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:25,080
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

105
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:26,970
<font color="yellow">Everyone around me does.</font>

106
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:32,270
<font color="yellow">Don't criticise me for being different from them.</font>

107
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,410
<font color="yellow">Does it look like I'm criticising you?</font>

108
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:37,710
<font color="yellow">I never criticised you.</font>

109
00:06:38,470 --> 00:06:39,910
<font color="yellow">I looked up to you.</font>

110
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:43,810
<font color="yellow">You're lucky you're so smart.</font>

111
00:07:03,010 --> 00:07:05,230
<font color="yellow">- You held a disciplinary meeting?
-  Yes.</font>

112
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:07,310
<font color="yellow">Was it necessary to make such a big deal out of this?</font>

113
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:08,530
<font color="yellow">You should've ignored it.</font>

114
00:07:08,530 --> 00:07:12,330
<font color="yellow">We have to make sure the employees are alert by showing an example.</font>

115
00:07:12,330 --> 00:07:13,340
<font color="yellow">Be careful.</font>

116
00:07:14,810 --> 00:07:17,170
<font color="yellow">I have a bad feeling about this situation.</font>

117
00:07:18,610 --> 00:07:21,070
<font color="yellow">I think it's since then.</font>

118
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:22,910
<font color="yellow">We took a big risk...</font>

119
00:07:23,470 --> 00:07:26,010
<font color="yellow">when we put the hospital through the tax investigation to get Doo Sik.</font>

120
00:07:26,010 --> 00:07:28,880
<font color="yellow">It's okay, Father. You've become soft.</font>

121
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,670
<font color="yellow">I wouldn't be who I am if it weren't for that.</font>

122
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:34,710
<font color="yellow">- Fine. Do a good job.
-  Okay.</font>

123
00:07:36,570 --> 00:07:38,250
<font color="yellow">The different levels of disciplinary action are...</font>

124
00:07:38,250 --> 00:07:40,870
<font color="yellow">warning, reduction in salary, suspension and termination.</font>

125
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:44,640
<font color="yellow">I believe a warning is enough for Dr Yoo.</font>

126
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:47,140
<font color="yellow">How can we do that when she's all over the media?</font>

127
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:49,110
<font color="yellow">She's not even showing any regret.</font>

128
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,850
<font color="yellow">We should fire her.</font>

129
00:07:50,850 --> 00:07:52,930
<font color="yellow">If we fire her for this, she can fight back...</font>

130
00:07:52,930 --> 00:07:56,280
<font color="yellow">that there is a problem in the disciplinary measures.</font>

131
00:07:56,280 --> 00:08:00,120
<font color="yellow">This is an issue for the entire Department of Neurosurgery.</font>

132
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,770
<font color="yellow">I don't think we should have an individual take all the blame.</font>

133
00:08:03,370 --> 00:08:05,740
<font color="yellow">Are you saying that because of your personal feelings for her?</font>

134
00:08:06,570 --> 00:08:08,740
<font color="yellow">You're the one who's letting your personal emotions take over.</font>

135
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,310
<font color="yellow">He's not picking up.</font>

136
00:08:20,570 --> 00:08:22,610
<font color="yellow">Have you eaten yet?</font>

137
00:08:23,710 --> 00:08:25,840
<font color="yellow">Is Kim Soo Kyeong's CT out yet?</font>

138
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:28,530
<font color="yellow">I'll take her over right now.</font>

139
00:08:28,530 --> 00:08:31,010
<font color="yellow">Your phone. Why do you never pick up?</font>

140
00:08:31,410 --> 00:08:34,460
<font color="yellow">You turned our department upside-down, so wake up!</font>

141
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:36,910
<font color="yellow">Did you forget again? What a moron.</font>

142
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:39,520
<font color="yellow">Focus on work, not your webtoon.</font>

143
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,010
<font color="yellow">Do you have time to waste?</font>

144
00:08:46,170 --> 00:08:49,160
<font color="yellow">That's weird. Why didn't he talk back?</font>

145
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,480
<font color="yellow">Stop it.</font>

146
00:08:50,980 --> 00:08:52,840
<font color="yellow">He must be dying inside.</font>

147
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:55,410
<font color="yellow">He adores Dr Yoo and he might have cut her career short.</font>

148
00:08:55,410 --> 00:08:57,100
<font color="yellow">I'll keep pushing him.</font>

149
00:08:57,100 --> 00:08:59,310
<font color="yellow">They're too laid back. That's why we have issues.</font>

150
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,940
<font color="yellow">- It's been a while.
-  Hello.</font>

151
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:17,100
<font color="yellow">I've been waiting. I am glad you finally called.</font>

152
00:09:17,100 --> 00:09:19,460
<font color="yellow">It feels good to be welcomed.</font>

153
00:09:19,460 --> 00:09:22,710
<font color="yellow">Thanks for making the trip. Do you want something to eat?</font>

154
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:23,740
<font color="yellow">My treat.</font>

155
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:24,870
<font color="yellow">No, it's fine.</font>

156
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:27,640
<font color="yellow">Thanks for being so kind.</font>

157
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,310
<font color="yellow">I wonder if...</font>

158
00:09:30,770 --> 00:09:34,090
<font color="yellow">your offer from last time is still on the table.</font>

159
00:09:34,090 --> 00:09:35,710
<font color="yellow">Of course it is.</font>

160
00:09:43,870 --> 00:09:45,610
<font color="yellow">(Hong Hong Hong)</font>

161
00:09:46,980 --> 00:09:48,210
<font color="yellow">Hello, Mr Hong.</font>

162
00:09:48,210 --> 00:09:51,370
<font color="yellow">I have two bits of good news and one bit of bad news. Are you free?</font>

163
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:55,770
<font color="yellow">Go on, then.</font>

164
00:09:56,410 --> 00:09:58,600
<font color="yellow">I want the good news first.</font>

165
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,440
<font color="yellow">I'll give you just one, then.</font>

166
00:10:00,980 --> 00:10:03,940
<font color="yellow">- Why?
-  Good things are hard to come by.</font>

167
00:10:04,810 --> 00:10:07,070
<font color="yellow">I want the giving tree back.</font>

168
00:10:07,070 --> 00:10:08,510
<font color="yellow">I miss my Daddy Long Legs.</font>

169
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:09,710
<font color="yellow">I won't go back.</font>

170
00:10:13,110 --> 00:10:14,240
<font color="yellow">The good news.</font>

171
00:10:15,570 --> 00:10:18,440
<font color="yellow">I will deliver the conclusion the disciplinary committee reached.</font>

172
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,070
<font color="yellow">It's best to hear it from me.</font>

173
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,940
<font color="yellow">That's true.</font>

174
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:25,010
<font color="yellow">What's that bad news?</font>

175
00:10:25,010 --> 00:10:26,110
<font color="yellow">The verdict.</font>

176
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:29,140
<font color="yellow">One month's suspension.</font>

177
00:10:31,770 --> 00:10:33,170
<font color="yellow">It's shorter than I thought.</font>

178
00:10:37,410 --> 00:10:38,740
<font color="yellow">You were great today.</font>

179
00:10:40,110 --> 00:10:42,740
<font color="yellow">I was so proud to be your boyfriend.</font>

180
00:10:43,210 --> 00:10:46,240
<font color="yellow">I was glad you asked the right questions.</font>

181
00:10:47,070 --> 00:10:49,710
<font color="yellow">I didn't want to be there just to accept punishment.</font>

182
00:10:50,710 --> 00:10:54,240
<font color="yellow">I wanted to show everyone how much I'd grown.</font>

183
00:10:56,310 --> 00:11:00,010
<font color="yellow">For the next bit of good news, we need a change of scenery.</font>

184
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,050
<font color="yellow">That's a deal.</font>

185
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:05,440
<font color="yellow">Who will look after Hee Young while I'm away?</font>

186
00:11:15,770 --> 00:11:18,090
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here? She isn't your patient.</font>

187
00:11:18,090 --> 00:11:19,840
<font color="yellow">Your patient is my patient.</font>

188
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,240
<font color="yellow">We never split duties.</font>

189
00:11:22,040 --> 00:11:23,840
<font color="yellow">You don't have to feel sorry.</font>

190
00:11:24,470 --> 00:11:26,040
<font color="yellow">I adjusted her IV drops.</font>

191
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:30,740
<font color="yellow">I only got one month's suspension.</font>

192
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,910
<font color="yellow">Take good care of her for me.</font>

193
00:11:44,410 --> 00:11:46,540
<font color="yellow">(Neurosurgery, Kang Kyung Joon)</font>

194
00:11:48,370 --> 00:11:49,710
<font color="yellow">- Kyung Joon.
-  Yes?</font>

195
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:52,370
<font color="yellow">Did you change Lee Soon Jin's dressing?</font>

196
00:11:52,370 --> 00:11:53,410
<font color="yellow">I told Kang Soo to.</font>

197
00:11:53,410 --> 00:11:55,640
<font color="yellow">Is that everyone's favourite catchphrase these days?</font>

198
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:57,140
<font color="yellow">What's wrong with you?</font>

199
00:11:57,140 --> 00:11:59,010
<font color="yellow">She has an infection. Do your job!</font>

200
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:00,810
<font color="yellow">I apologise.</font>

201
00:12:00,810 --> 00:12:02,100
<font color="yellow">Is that it?</font>

202
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:03,510
<font color="yellow">I'll get right to it.</font>

203
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:10,280
<font color="yellow">This is why the residents are in such a mess.</font>

204
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:13,240
<font color="yellow">One forgot a call he got, and another ran away.</font>

205
00:12:13,570 --> 00:12:15,140
<font color="yellow">Where did things start to go wrong?</font>

206
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:18,370
<font color="yellow">Kang Kyung Joon. How dare you call yourself a chief.</font>

207
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:25,140
<font color="yellow">It's all my fault, Doctor.</font>

208
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,220
<font color="yellow">He did nothing wrong.</font>

209
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,710
<font color="yellow">Shut your mouth.</font>

