00:13:44,610 --> 00:13:46,710
<font color="yellow">(Choi Kang Soo)</font>

235
00:13:49,910 --> 00:13:51,110
<font color="yellow">What do you see?</font>

236
00:13:51,110 --> 00:13:53,570
<font color="yellow">A meningioma by his sphenoid bone.</font>

237
00:13:54,170 --> 00:13:55,210
