00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:16,870
<font color="yellow">but he collapsed at our party after one drink.</font>

247
00:14:18,070 --> 00:14:19,140
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

248
00:14:19,640 --> 00:14:21,610
<font color="yellow">Sharing witness accounts?</font>

249
00:14:25,010 --> 00:14:26,240
<font color="yellow">I wonder if he's awake.</font>

250
00:14:33,970 --> 00:14:35,040
<font color="yellow">How do you feel?</font>

251
00:14:36,140 --> 00:14:37,340
<font color="yellow">Stay in bed.</font>

252
00:14:41,170 --> 00:14:42,170
<font color="yellow">Are you embarrassed?</font>

