295
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:02,310
<font color="yellow">Complain as you might. But there's no place like home.</font>

296
00:17:05,570 --> 00:17:08,370
<font color="yellow">If I can't get rid of the company, I might as well enjoy it.</font>

297
00:17:10,180 --> 00:17:11,410
<font color="yellow">Where's In Joo?</font>

298
00:17:11,410 --> 00:17:13,350
<font color="yellow">She went to her own home.</font>

299
00:17:13,350 --> 00:17:14,810
<font color="yellow">The renovation's done.</font>

