00:17:16,810 --> 00:17:18,370
<font color="yellow">I heard what's going on.</font>

302
00:17:19,210 --> 00:17:20,540
<font color="yellow">It must be hard on Ji Hong.</font>

303
00:17:22,310 --> 00:17:23,510
<font color="yellow">Dr Yoo's tough.</font>

