00:17:26,240 --> 00:17:28,110
<font color="yellow">A month's break can be good for her.</font>

306
00:17:29,210 --> 00:17:31,310
<font color="yellow">How did you end up falling for Ji Hong's girlfriend?</font>

307
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,310
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

308
00:17:34,740 --> 00:17:36,680
<font color="yellow">Find someone else.</font>

309
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:40,340
<font color="yellow">I'll scour all the girls I know and set you up with the prettiest.</font>

