00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,710
<font color="yellow">Forget it.</font>

311
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:44,060
<font color="yellow">I haven't felt like this in a while.</font>

312
00:17:44,060 --> 00:17:47,070
<font color="yellow">Love is a hard emotion to come by.</font>

313
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,340
<font color="yellow">How deep is it?</font>

