00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:56,470
<font color="yellow">I do. I hate it, too.</font>

317
00:17:57,210 --> 00:18:01,470
<font color="yellow">I'm actually considering joining the board of directors for her.</font>

318
00:18:01,810 --> 00:18:02,810
<font color="yellow">Why?</font>

319
00:18:02,810 --> 00:18:05,410
<font color="yellow">I don't want her to ever have to go through that again.</font>

320
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:07,970
<font color="yellow">Ji Hong should watch out, then.</font>

321
00:18:27,010 --> 00:18:28,680
<font color="yellow">This is exactly the kind of moment I wanted to go home...</font>

322
00:18:29,940 --> 00:18:31,740
<font color="yellow">when I was out here fishing with my father.</font>

323
00:18:33,370 --> 00:18:34,680
<font color="yellow">When you couldn't catch any fish?</font>

324
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,740
<font color="yellow">No, I just hate long silence. It's not for me.</font>

325
00:18:37,370 --> 00:18:38,570
<font color="yellow">I had to keep doing things.</font>

326
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:43,910
<font color="yellow">But now, I like sitting here and doing nothing like this.</font>

327
00:18:44,410 --> 00:18:46,410
<font color="yellow">I can understand why Father used to like going fishing.</font>

328
00:18:47,710 --> 00:18:50,710
<font color="yellow">Why is it that people always begin to understand each other better...</font>

329
00:18:51,180 --> 00:18:53,350
<font color="yellow">after they part ways than when they were together?</font>

330
00:18:53,350 --> 00:18:54,740
<font color="yellow">Be good to people before they leave you.</font>

331
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,440
<font color="yellow">Be good to me when I'm still around.</font>

332
00:18:57,940 --> 00:18:58,970
<font color="yellow">Yes, Sir!</font>

333
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:02,640
<font color="yellow">The second good news.</font>

