00:19:04,570 --> 00:19:06,370
<font color="yellow">Dr Kim Chi Hyun proposed a deal.</font>

335
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:10,940
<font color="yellow">What does he want in return for the anaesthesiology report?</font>

336
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:15,310
<font color="yellow">I suggested an alternative instead of accepting his request.</font>

337
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:17,940
<font color="yellow">I'm waiting for him to consider it and accept it at the moment.</font>

338
00:19:19,370 --> 00:19:22,010
<font color="yellow">If he says no to it, I'll make him say yes.</font>

339
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:25,440
<font color="yellow">I'll take care of it. All you need to do...</font>

