00:19:26,180 --> 00:19:28,340
<font color="yellow">is to wait for me to get the anaesthesiology report,</font>

341
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:30,580
<font color="yellow">take it to President Jin and make him apologise to you...</font>

342
00:19:30,580 --> 00:19:32,110
<font color="yellow">then take your hands off of it altogether.</font>

343
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,680
<font color="yellow">Ms Kang...</font>

