00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:05,180
<font color="yellow">Your grandmother got on her knees in front of me...</font>

345
00:20:06,870 --> 00:20:08,310
<font color="yellow">to ask me to take good care of you.</font>

346
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:12,470
