00:20:17,570 --> 00:20:18,680
<font color="yellow">You are.</font>

348
00:20:27,470 --> 00:20:28,510
<font color="yellow">Do you know what this is?</font>

349
00:20:30,910 --> 00:20:33,240
<font color="yellow">It was always hung onto your bag.</font>

350
00:20:36,010 --> 00:20:38,370
<font color="yellow">It's a key chain I used to use before the accident.</font>

351
00:20:43,180 --> 00:20:44,210
<font color="yellow">My parents...</font>

352
00:20:45,810 --> 00:20:47,140
<font color="yellow">didn't have to die then.</font>

353
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:50,410
<font color="yellow">They missed the golden hour because of people.</font>

354
00:20:51,340 --> 00:20:54,740
<font color="yellow">I really wanted to wipe out the entire world then.</font>

355
00:20:57,470 --> 00:20:59,470
<font color="yellow">My family used to be very happy together.</font>

356
00:21:00,910 --> 00:21:03,010
<font color="yellow">Grandma and I were happy together too...</font>

357
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:05,110
<font color="yellow">before she got the surgery.</font>

358
00:21:05,110 --> 00:21:06,840
<font color="yellow">I don't believe in tomorrow.</font>

359
00:21:08,010 --> 00:21:09,910
<font color="yellow">This moment right now is the only thing that matters to me...</font>

360
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:12,440
<font color="yellow">because we might die tomorrow.</font>

361
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:18,540
<font color="yellow">What Ms Kang wants is for you to be happy,</font>

