00:21:20,940 --> 00:21:24,310
<font color="yellow">not for you to give up today to find out the truth about her death.</font>

363
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:28,410
<font color="yellow">To me, that's the reason I live today.</font>

364
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:30,710
<font color="yellow">Yes. That's why I'm trying to help you.</font>

