00:23:36,310 --> 00:23:39,640
<font color="yellow">We can do it at night, too. Let me know when is the best for you.</font>

396
00:23:51,640 --> 00:23:52,670
<font color="yellow">(Neurosurgery, Jung Yoon Do)</font>

397
00:23:54,010 --> 00:23:55,370
<font color="yellow">(Neurosurgery, Hong Ji Hong)</font>

398
00:24:01,910 --> 00:24:04,040
<font color="yellow">(Office of Vice President)</font>

