00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:04,830
<font color="yellow">Of course. Make your decision after careful consideration.</font>

415
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:06,440
<font color="yellow">It'll affect the next 20 years of your life.</font>

416
00:25:17,140 --> 00:25:19,170
